dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Rock County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NRock_Addresses_2018.gdbN. [The address point feature class was created to assist 911 dispatchers/calltakers in locating wireless E911 callers. Sources include: current aerial photography, NAIP aerial mosaic imagery, parcel maps, limited GPS collection and physical verification when necessary.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
